text: Grand Slam (2023) was a professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on September 20, 2023 at Arthur Ashe Stadium in Flushing, Queens, New York. The event aired as special episodes of Dynamite and Rampage respectively. It was the third Grand Slam event held by AEW. The main event of Dynamite saw MJF defeat Samoa Joe to keep his AEW World Championship. The main event of Rampage saw The Elite (Matt Jackson, Nick Jackson, and "Hangman" Adam Page) defeat Mogul Embassy (Brian Cage, Bishop Kaun, and Toa Liona) in a six-man tag team match to win the ROH
